<div class="email-container">
  <h1>EGYM Genius – Here's What's New!</h1>
<img alt="Header Image" class="header-image" src="https://de.egym.com/sites/default/files/2025-05/HeroMedium_LP_GENIUS_EN_mobilex2.jpg" style="width: 600px; height: auto; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin: auto;"/>
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
<tr><td style="border-top: 1px solid #ffffff; padding: 10px 0;"></td></tr>
</table>
<p style="font-size:14px; color:#160707; margin:0 0 10px;">    
We’re excited to share the latest EGYM Genius improvements with you. Here’s a quick overview of what’s been improved since our last update, plus a sneak peek at what’s coming next.<br/><br/>Note: To see these updates, please ensure the BMA and/or the Trainer App is up to date.
 <br/>
 <br/>
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
<tr><td style="border-top: 1px solid #dddddd; padding: 10px 0;"></td></tr>
</table>
  <h2>Improved EGYM Genius compatibility with Matrix equipment</h2>
<p style="font-size:14px; color:#160707; margin:0 0 10px;">
We’ve improved Genius compatibility with the Matrix Aura (remeasured) and Matrix Go series. Genius now delivers even more precise weight predictions, and machine settings — helping your members work out smarter and more effectively.
<h4>New compatible vendor lines:</h4>
<ul style="font-size:14px; color:#160707; padding-left:20px; margin:10px 0;">
<li>Matrix Aura (33/38) remeasured (for EU and US [imperial])  </li>
<li>Matrix Go Series (10/11) (for EU)  </li>
</ul>
 <br/>
    <img alt="preview Image" class="header-image" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/egymproductnews/newsletter-images/refs/heads/main/Genius/EN%20Mails/EN%20Images/genius-matrix-compatible.png" style="width: 600px; height: auto; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin: auto; border-radius: 5px;"/>
  <p><em>This is a visual example only. All Matrix Aura models (33/38) and Matrix Go Series models (10/11) are included.</em></p>
  <br/>
  <h2>Genius for Trainers: Location-based equipment categories</h2>
<p style="font-size:14px; color:#160707; margin:0 0 10px;">
We’ve optimized the summary page of personalized training plans in the Trainer App.
Genius now only shows excluded equipment categories that are relevant to your gym location.
 <br/> <br/>
This means less manual editing, fewer errors, and greater efficiency in creating training plans – especially helpful for gyms with multiple locations and different equipment setups.
 <br/><br/>
  <img alt="preview Image" class="header-image" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/egymproductnews/newsletter-images/refs/heads/main/Genius/EN%20Mails/EN%20Images/genius-trainer-app-summary-page.png" style="width: 600px; height: auto; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin: auto; border-radius: 5px;"/>
  <br/>
  <h2>Coming soon (4-6 weeks): Adjustable training plans</h2>
<p style="font-size:14px; color:#160707; margin:0 0 10px;">
Personal trainers and members will soon be able to fine-tune the mix of strength, cardio, and flexibility in each personalized training plan – directly in the Trainer and Member App, respectively!
 <br/> <br/>
Behind the scenes, Genius smartly adjusts weekly workout splits and muscle focus based on each member’s goals and recent activity, keeping plans balanced, personalized, and effective over time.
 <br/><br/>
    <img alt="preview Image" class="header-image" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/egymproductnews/newsletter-images/refs/heads/main/Genius/EN%20Mails/EN%20Images/genius-trainer-app-adjustable-goals.png" style="width: 600px; height: auto; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin: auto; border-radius: 5px;"/>
  <br/>
    <h2>Coming soon (4-6 weeks): AI-powered suggestions</h2>
<p style="font-size:14px; color:#160707; margin:0 0 10px;">
Genius will automatically suggest weights, sets, reps, and rest times for exercises that PTs manually add or edit. This helps them create high-quality, science-based training plans faster, saves time, and improves the workout experience for your members.
 <br/><br/>
    <img alt="preview Image" class="header-image" src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/egymproductnews/newsletter-images/refs/heads/main/Genius/EN%20Mails/EN%20Images/genius-trainer-app-ai-powered-suggestions-rep.png" style="width: 600px; height: auto; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin: auto; border-radius: 5px;"/>

